caption.text: It’s been a while since I’ve done one of these 🧚‍♀️❤️ name letters £4 per doll 💖
Fresh feeling folk 👩‍🎨💖
Army daddy 💖❤️🎁 perfect little custom bespoke painted doll just for you 🧚‍♀️ pop me a message with your ideas and I’ll create you your own special peg! 😊

My lovely bestie took this photo today it’s just so sweet - these were for her Neices 4th birthday and what could be better! Birthday cake 🍰, sunshine ☀️ and fairytale folk! 🎁💖 #underthesea #smallworldplay #imaginationtime
Decided to make MORE Halloween Folk 👻 🎃 🧙🏽‍♀️ 1-2 weeks dispatch time - order yours on www.etsy.co.uk/shop/fairytalefolkdorset 👩‍🎨 £24 plus p & p 🎃🎃BOO !

I’ve had a painting folkies break today and instead we have , built Lilyrose Cottage ! Soooo much pink and white paint all over the lawn... and the dog .... but hey it was worth it 💖 #daughterlove #playhouse #thinkpink
Portrait peg dolls 💖👩‍🎨 all from photos ❤️🎁

Unique Christmas gifts 🎁 personalised hanging decorations 🎅🏻 £6.50 each 🎄 my order book is filling fast, current lead time is 10 weeks pop me a message or check out my Etsy shop to order 🧚‍♀️ #handmade #pegdolls #christmasgiftsideas
Personalised Christmas decs in construction 😇 🎄 🎅🏻 gorgeous gold hooks to add in and a selection of felt fairy wings to add 💖👩‍🎨
Grain of the wood - I love the patterns in the world, organic fibres are their best 💖
1am... still going strong... 🥱🥱🥱 ... shes says falling asleep on her folkies!!!! 😴😴😴 #needsleep #workingmumlifebalance

So I’ve finally taken the time to get instagram sorted! I know I know i am literally how late to the party ?!?! My excuse I’m on the wrong side of my thirties and instagram has never appealed but alas business needs must ( I think?!?) so come check me out @fairytalefolkdorset 🥳🤩👩‍🎨
